title: Administrative Assistant Interview
Application Type: I applied through other source. I interviewed at Association of Home Appliance Manufacturers (Washington, DC)
Interview Descriptions: I applied for a job at the association after finding a listing in the Washington Post. I sent an email with my resume and I got an email about a week later asking to come in. I met with the President/CEO and one of the VPs that I would be reporting to on the first visit. I received another email asking to come back for second interview with another VP that I would also be reporting to. The whole process took about 2 1/2 weeks from submission of resume to offer. After the second interview, I had to create a mail merge as part of my skills test.
Interview Questions: Do I have experience creating web pages?
